6736
6737union power_info {
6738 struct _ATOM_POWERPLAY_INFO info;
6739 struct _ATOM_POWERPLAY_INFO_V2 info_2;
6740 struct _ATOM_POWERPLAY_INFO_V3 info_3;
6741 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_POWERPLAYTABLE pplib;
6742 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_POWERPLAYTABLE2 pplib2;
6743 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_POWERPLAYTABLE3 pplib3;
6744};
6745
6746union pplib_clock_info {
6747 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_R600_CLOCK_INFO r600;
6748 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_RS780_CLOCK_INFO rs780;
6749 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_EVERGREEN_CLOCK_INFO evergreen;
6750 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_SUMO_CLOCK_INFO sumo;
6751 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_SI_CLOCK_INFO si;
6752};
6753
6754union pplib_power_state {
6755 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_STATE v1;
6756 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_STATE_V2 v2;
6757};
6758
6759static void si_parse_pplib_non_clock_info(struct radeon_device *rdev,
6760 struct radeon_ps *rps,
6761 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_NONCLOCK_INFO *non_clock_info,
6762 u8 table_rev)
6763{
6764 rps->caps = le32_to_cpu(non_clock_info->ulCapsAndSettings);
6765 rps->class = le16_to_cpu(non_clock_info->usClassification);
6766 rps->class2 = le16_to_cpu(non_clock_info->usClassification2);
6767
6768 if (ATOM_PPLIB_NONCLOCKINFO_VER1 < table_rev) {
6769 rps->vclk = le32_to_cpu(non_clock_info->ulVCLK);
6770 rps->dclk = le32_to_cpu(non_clock_info->ulDCLK);
6771 } else if (r600_is_uvd_state(rps->class, rps->class2)) {
6772 rps->vclk = RV770_DEFAULT_VCLK_FREQ;
6773 rps->dclk = RV770_DEFAULT_DCLK_FREQ;
6774 } else {
6775 rps->vclk = 0;
6776 rps->dclk = 0;
6777 }
6778
6779 if (rps->class & ATOM_PPLIB_CLASSIFICATION_BOOT)
6780 rdev->pm.dpm.boot_ps = rps;
6781 if (rps->class & ATOM_PPLIB_CLASSIFICATION_UVDSTATE)
6782 rdev->pm.dpm.uvd_ps = rps;
6783}
6784
6785static void si_parse_pplib_clock_info(struct radeon_device *rdev,
6786 struct radeon_ps *rps, int index,
6787 union pplib_clock_info *clock_info)
6788{
6789 struct rv7xx_power_info *pi = rv770_get_pi(rdev);
6790 struct evergreen_power_info *eg_pi = evergreen_get_pi(rdev);
6791 struct si_power_info *si_pi = si_get_pi(rdev);
6792 struct ni_ps *ps = ni_get_ps(rps);
6793 u16 leakage_voltage;
6794 struct rv7xx_pl *pl = &ps->performance_levels[index];
6795 int ret;
6796
6797 ps->performance_level_count = index + 1;
6798
6799 pl->sclk = le16_to_cpu(clock_info->si.usEngineClockLow);
6800 pl->sclk |= clock_info->si.ucEngineClockHigh << 16;
6801 pl->mclk = le16_to_cpu(clock_info->si.usMemoryClockLow);
6802 pl->mclk |= clock_info->si.ucMemoryClockHigh << 16;
6803
6804 pl->vddc = le16_to_cpu(clock_info->si.usVDDC);
6805 pl->vddci = le16_to_cpu(clock_info->si.usVDDCI);
6806 pl->flags = le32_to_cpu(clock_info->si.ulFlags);
6807 pl->pcie_gen = r600_get_pcie_gen_support(rdev,
6808 si_pi->sys_pcie_mask,
6809 si_pi->boot_pcie_gen,
6810 clock_info->si.ucPCIEGen);
6811
6812 /* patch up vddc if necessary */
6813 ret = si_get_leakage_voltage_from_leakage_index(rdev, pl->vddc,
6814 &leakage_voltage);
6815 if (ret == 0)
6816 pl->vddc = leakage_voltage;
6817
6818 if (rps->class & ATOM_PPLIB_CLASSIFICATION_ACPI) {
6819 pi->acpi_vddc = pl->vddc;
6820 eg_pi->acpi_vddci = pl->vddci;
6821 si_pi->acpi_pcie_gen = pl->pcie_gen;
6822 }
6823
6824 if ((rps->class2 & ATOM_PPLIB_CLASSIFICATION2_ULV) &&
6825 index == 0) {
6826 /* XXX disable for A0 tahiti */
6827 si_pi->ulv.supported = false;
6828 si_pi->ulv.pl = *pl;
6829 si_pi->ulv.one_pcie_lane_in_ulv = false;
6830 si_pi->ulv.volt_change_delay = SISLANDS_ULVVOLTAGECHANGEDELAY_DFLT;
6831 si_pi->ulv.cg_ulv_parameter = SISLANDS_CGULVPARAMETER_DFLT;
6832 si_pi->ulv.cg_ulv_control = SISLANDS_CGULVCONTROL_DFLT;
6833 }
6834
6835 if (pi->min_vddc_in_table > pl->vddc)
6836 pi->min_vddc_in_table = pl->vddc;
6837
6838 if (pi->max_vddc_in_table < pl->vddc)
6839 pi->max_vddc_in_table = pl->vddc;
6840
6841 /* patch up boot state */
6842 if (rps->class & ATOM_PPLIB_CLASSIFICATION_BOOT) {
6843 u16 vddc, vddci, mvdd;
6844 radeon_atombios_get_default_voltages(rdev, &vddc, &vddci, &mvdd);
6845 pl->mclk = rdev->clock.default_mclk;
6846 pl->sclk = rdev->clock.default_sclk;
6847 pl->vddc = vddc;
6848 pl->vddci = vddci;
6849 si_pi->mvdd_bootup_value = mvdd;
6850 }
6851
6852 if ((rps->class & ATOM_PPLIB_CLASSIFICATION_UI_MASK) ==
6853 ATOM_PPLIB_CLASSIFICATION_UI_PERFORMANCE) {
6854 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.max_clock_voltage_on_ac.sclk = pl->sclk;
6855 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.max_clock_voltage_on_ac.mclk = pl->mclk;
6856 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.max_clock_voltage_on_ac.vddc = pl->vddc;
6857 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.max_clock_voltage_on_ac.vddci = pl->vddci;
6858 }
6859}
6860
6861static int si_parse_power_table(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6862{
6863 struct radeon_mode_info *mode_info = &rdev->mode_info;
6864 struct _ATOM_PPLIB_NONCLOCK_INFO *non_clock_info;
6865 union pplib_power_state *power_state;
6866 int i, j, k, non_clock_array_index, clock_array_index;
6867 union pplib_clock_info *clock_info;
6868 struct _StateArray *state_array;
6869 struct _ClockInfoArray *clock_info_array;
6870 struct _NonClockInfoArray *non_clock_info_array;
6871 union power_info *power_info;
6872 int index = GetIndexIntoMasterTable(DATA, PowerPlayInfo);
6873 u16 data_offset;
6874 u8 frev, crev;
6875 u8 *power_state_offset;
6876 struct ni_ps *ps;
6877
6878 if (!atom_parse_data_header(mode_info->atom_context, index, NULL,
6879 &frev, &crev, &data_offset))
6880 return -EINVAL;
6881 power_info = (union power_info *)(mode_info->atom_context->bios + data_offset);
6882
6883 state_array = (struct _StateArray *)
6884 (mode_info->atom_context->bios + data_offset +
6885 le16_to_cpu(power_info->pplib.usStateArrayOffset));
6886 clock_info_array = (struct _ClockInfoArray *)
6887 (mode_info->atom_context->bios + data_offset +
6888 le16_to_cpu(power_info->pplib.usClockInfoArrayOffset));
6889 non_clock_info_array = (struct _NonClockInfoArray *)
6890 (mode_info->atom_context->bios + data_offset +
6891 le16_to_cpu(power_info->pplib.usNonClockInfoArrayOffset));
6892
6893 rdev->pm.dpm.ps = kzalloc(sizeof(struct radeon_ps) *
6894 state_array->ucNumEntries, GFP_KERNEL);
6895 if (!rdev->pm.dpm.ps)
6896 return -ENOMEM;
6897 power_state_offset = (u8 *)state_array->states;
6898 for (i = 0; i < state_array->ucNumEntries; i++) {
6899 u8 *idx;
6900 power_state = (union pplib_power_state *)power_state_offset;
6901 non_clock_array_index = power_state->v2.nonClockInfoIndex;
6902 non_clock_info = (struct _ATOM_PPLIB_NONCLOCK_INFO *)
6903 &non_clock_info_array->nonClockInfo[non_clock_array_index];
6904 if (!rdev->pm.power_state[i].clock_info)
6905 return -EINVAL;
6906 ps = kzalloc(sizeof(struct ni_ps), GFP_KERNEL);
6907 if (ps == NULL) {
6908 kfree(rdev->pm.dpm.ps);
6909 return -ENOMEM;
6910 }
6911 rdev->pm.dpm.ps[i].ps_priv = ps;
6912 si_parse_pplib_non_clock_info(rdev, &rdev->pm.dpm.ps[i],
6913 non_clock_info,
6914 non_clock_info_array->ucEntrySize);
6915 k = 0;
6916 idx = (u8 *)&power_state->v2.clockInfoIndex[0];
6917 for (j = 0; j < power_state->v2.ucNumDPMLevels; j++) {
6918 clock_array_index = idx[j];
6919 if (clock_array_index >= clock_info_array->ucNumEntries)
6920 continue;
6921 if (k >= SISLANDS_MAX_HARDWARE_POWERLEVELS)
6922 break;
6923 clock_info = (union pplib_clock_info *)
6924 ((u8 *)&clock_info_array->clockInfo[0] +
6925 (clock_array_index * clock_info_array->ucEntrySize));
6926 si_parse_pplib_clock_info(rdev,
6927 &rdev->pm.dpm.ps[i], k,
6928 clock_info);
6929 k++;
6930 }
6931 power_state_offset += 2 + power_state->v2.ucNumDPMLevels;
6932 }
6933 rdev->pm.dpm.num_ps = state_array->ucNumEntries;
6934
6935 /* fill in the vce power states */
6936 for (i = 0; i < RADEON_MAX_VCE_LEVELS; i++) {
6937 u32 sclk, mclk;
6938 clock_array_index = rdev->pm.dpm.vce_states[i].clk_idx;
6939 clock_info = (union pplib_clock_info *)
6940 &clock_info_array->clockInfo[clock_array_index * clock_info_array->ucEntrySize];
6941 sclk = le16_to_cpu(clock_info->si.usEngineClockLow);
6942 sclk |= clock_info->si.ucEngineClockHigh << 16;
6943 mclk = le16_to_cpu(clock_info->si.usMemoryClockLow);
6944 mclk |= clock_info->si.ucMemoryClockHigh << 16;
6945 rdev->pm.dpm.vce_states[i].sclk = sclk;
6946 rdev->pm.dpm.vce_states[i].mclk = mclk;
6947 }
6948
6949 return 0;
6950}
6951
6952int si_dpm_init(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6953{
6954 struct rv7xx_power_info *pi;
6955 struct evergreen_power_info *eg_pi;
6956 struct ni_power_info *ni_pi;
6957 struct si_power_info *si_pi;
6958 struct atom_clock_dividers dividers;
6959 int ret;
6960#ifndef __NetBSD__ /* XXX radeon pcie */
6961 u32 mask;
6962#endif
6963
6964 si_pi = kzalloc(sizeof(struct si_power_info), GFP_KERNEL);
6965 if (si_pi == NULL)
6966 return -ENOMEM;
6967 rdev->pm.dpm.priv = si_pi;
6968 ni_pi = &si_pi->ni;
6969 eg_pi = &ni_pi->eg;
6970 pi = &eg_pi->rv7xx;
6971
6972#ifndef __NetBSD__ /* XXX radeon pcie */
6973 ret = drm_pcie_get_speed_cap_mask(rdev->ddev, &mask);
6974 if (ret)
6975 si_pi->sys_pcie_mask = 0;
6976 else
6977 si_pi->sys_pcie_mask = mask;
6978#endif
6979 si_pi->force_pcie_gen = RADEON_PCIE_GEN_INVALID;
6980 si_pi->boot_pcie_gen = si_get_current_pcie_speed(rdev);
6981
6982 si_set_max_cu_value(rdev);
6983
6984 rv770_get_max_vddc(rdev);
6985 si_get_leakage_vddc(rdev);
6986 si_patch_dependency_tables_based_on_leakage(rdev);
6987
6988 pi->acpi_vddc = 0;
6989 eg_pi->acpi_vddci = 0;
6990 pi->min_vddc_in_table = 0;
6991 pi->max_vddc_in_table = 0;
6992
6993 ret = r600_get_platform_caps(rdev);
6994 if (ret)
6995 return ret;
6996
6997 ret = r600_parse_extended_power_table(rdev);
6998 if (ret)
6999 return ret;
7000
7001 ret = si_parse_power_table(rdev);
7002 if (ret)
7003 return ret;
7004
7005 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries =
7006 kzalloc(4 * sizeof(struct radeon_clock_voltage_dependency_entry), GFP_KERNEL);
7007 if (!rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries) {
7008 r600_free_extended_power_table(rdev);
7009 return -ENOMEM;
7010 }
7011 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.count = 4;
7012 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries[0].clk = 0;
7013 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries[0].v = 0;
7014 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries[1].clk = 36000;
7015 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries[1].v = 720;
7016 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries[2].clk = 54000;
7017 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries[2].v = 810;
7018 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries[3].clk = 72000;
7019 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries[3].v = 900;
7020
7021 if (rdev->pm.dpm.voltage_response_time == 0)
7022 rdev->pm.dpm.voltage_response_time = R600_VOLTAGERESPONSETIME_DFLT;
7023 if (rdev->pm.dpm.backbias_response_time == 0)
7024 rdev->pm.dpm.backbias_response_time = R600_BACKBIASRESPONSETIME_DFLT;
7025
7026 ret = radeon_atom_get_clock_dividers(rdev, COMPUTE_ENGINE_PLL_PARAM,
7027 0, false, &dividers);
7028 if (ret)
7029 pi->ref_div = dividers.ref_div + 1;
7030 else
7031 pi->ref_div = R600_REFERENCEDIVIDER_DFLT;
7032
7033 eg_pi->smu_uvd_hs = false;
7034
7035 pi->mclk_strobe_mode_threshold = 40000;
7036 if (si_is_special_1gb_platform(rdev))
7037 pi->mclk_stutter_mode_threshold = 0;
7038 else
7039 pi->mclk_stutter_mode_threshold = pi->mclk_strobe_mode_threshold;
7040 pi->mclk_edc_enable_threshold = 40000;
7041 eg_pi->mclk_edc_wr_enable_threshold = 40000;
7042
7043 ni_pi->mclk_rtt_mode_threshold = eg_pi->mclk_edc_wr_enable_threshold;
7044
7045 pi->voltage_control =
7046 radeon_atom_is_voltage_gpio(rdev, SET_VOLTAGE_TYPE_ASIC_VDDC,
7047 VOLTAGE_OBJ_GPIO_LUT);
7048 if (!pi->voltage_control) {
7049 si_pi->voltage_control_svi2 =
7050 radeon_atom_is_voltage_gpio(rdev, SET_VOLTAGE_TYPE_ASIC_VDDC,
7051 VOLTAGE_OBJ_SVID2);
7052 if (si_pi->voltage_control_svi2)
7053 radeon_atom_get_svi2_info(rdev, SET_VOLTAGE_TYPE_ASIC_VDDC,
7054 &si_pi->svd_gpio_id, &si_pi->svc_gpio_id);
7055 }
7056
7057 pi->mvdd_control =
7058 radeon_atom_is_voltage_gpio(rdev, SET_VOLTAGE_TYPE_ASIC_MVDDC,
7059 VOLTAGE_OBJ_GPIO_LUT);
7060
7061 eg_pi->vddci_control =
7062 radeon_atom_is_voltage_gpio(rdev, SET_VOLTAGE_TYPE_ASIC_VDDCI,
7063 VOLTAGE_OBJ_GPIO_LUT);
7064 if (!eg_pi->vddci_control)
7065 si_pi->vddci_control_svi2 =
7066 radeon_atom_is_voltage_gpio(rdev, SET_VOLTAGE_TYPE_ASIC_VDDCI,
7067 VOLTAGE_OBJ_SVID2);
7068
7069 si_pi->vddc_phase_shed_control =
7070 radeon_atom_is_voltage_gpio(rdev, SET_VOLTAGE_TYPE_ASIC_VDDC,
7071 VOLTAGE_OBJ_PHASE_LUT);
7072
7073 rv770_get_engine_memory_ss(rdev);
7074
7075 pi->asi = RV770_ASI_DFLT;
7076 pi->pasi = CYPRESS_HASI_DFLT;
7077 pi->vrc = SISLANDS_VRC_DFLT;
7078
7079 pi->gfx_clock_gating = true;
7080
7081 eg_pi->sclk_deep_sleep = true;
7082 si_pi->sclk_deep_sleep_above_low = false;
7083
7084 if (rdev->pm.int_thermal_type != THERMAL_TYPE_NONE)
7085 pi->thermal_protection = true;
7086 else
7087 pi->thermal_protection = false;
7088
7089 eg_pi->dynamic_ac_timing = true;
7090
7091 eg_pi->light_sleep = true;
7092#if defined(CONFIG_ACPI)
7093 eg_pi->pcie_performance_request =
7094 radeon_acpi_is_pcie_performance_request_supported(rdev);
7095#else
7096 eg_pi->pcie_performance_request = false;
7097#endif
7098
7099 si_pi->sram_end = SMC_RAM_END;
7100
7101 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.mclk_sclk_ratio = 4;
7102 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.sclk_mclk_delta = 15000;
7103 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_vddci_delta = 200;
7104 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.valid_sclk_values.count = 0;
7105 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.valid_sclk_values.values = NULL;
7106 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.valid_mclk_values.count = 0;
7107 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.valid_mclk_values.values = NULL;
7108
7109 si_initialize_powertune_defaults(rdev);
7110
7111 /* make sure dc limits are valid */
7112 if ((rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.max_clock_voltage_on_dc.sclk == 0) ||
7113 (rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.max_clock_voltage_on_dc.mclk == 0))
7114 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.max_clock_voltage_on_dc =
7115 rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.max_clock_voltage_on_ac;
7116
7117 si_pi->fan_ctrl_is_in_default_mode = true;
7118
7119 return 0;
7120}
7121
7122void si_dpm_fini(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7123{
7124 int i;
7125
7126 for (i = 0; i < rdev->pm.dpm.num_ps; i++) {
7127 kfree(rdev->pm.dpm.ps[i].ps_priv);
7128 }
7129 kfree(rdev->pm.dpm.ps);
7130 kfree(rdev->pm.dpm.priv);
7131 kfree(rdev->pm.dpm.dyn_state.vddc_dependency_on_dispclk.entries);
7132 r600_free_extended_power_table(rdev);
7133}
7134
7135#ifdef CONFIG_DEBUG_FS
7136void si_dpm_debugfs_print_current_performance_level(struct radeon_device *rdev,
7137 struct seq_file *m)
7138{
7139 struct evergreen_power_info *eg_pi = evergreen_get_pi(rdev);
7140 struct radeon_ps *rps = &eg_pi->current_rps;
7141 struct ni_ps *ps = ni_get_ps(rps);
7142 struct rv7xx_pl *pl;
7143 u32 current_index =
7144 (RREG32(TARGET_AND_CURRENT_PROFILE_INDEX) & CURRENT_STATE_INDEX_MASK) >>
7145 CURRENT_STATE_INDEX_SHIFT;
7146
7147 if (current_index >= ps->performance_level_count) {
7148 seq_printf(m, "invalid dpm profile %d\n", current_index);
7149 } else {
7150 pl = &ps->performance_levels[current_index];
7151 seq_printf(m, "uvd vclk: %d dclk: %d\n", rps->vclk, rps->dclk);
7152 seq_printf(m, "power level %d sclk: %u mclk: %u vddc: %u vddci: %u pcie gen: %u\n",
7153 current_index, pl->sclk, pl->mclk, pl->vddc, pl->vddci, pl->pcie_gen + 1);
7154 }
7155}
7156#endif
7157
7158u32 si_dpm_get_current_sclk(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7159{
7160 struct evergreen_power_info *eg_pi = evergreen_get_pi(rdev);
7161 struct radeon_ps *rps = &eg_pi->current_rps;
7162 struct ni_ps *ps = ni_get_ps(rps);
7163 struct rv7xx_pl *pl;
7164 u32 current_index =
7165 (RREG32(TARGET_AND_CURRENT_PROFILE_INDEX) & CURRENT_STATE_INDEX_MASK) >>
7166 CURRENT_STATE_INDEX_SHIFT;
7167
7168 if (current_index >= ps->performance_level_count) {
7169 return 0;
7170 } else {
7171 pl = &ps->performance_levels[current_index];
7172 return pl->sclk;
7173 }
7174}
7175
7176u32 si_dpm_get_current_mclk(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7177{
7178 struct evergreen_power_info *eg_pi = evergreen_get_pi(rdev);
7179 struct radeon_ps *rps = &eg_pi->current_rps;
7180 struct ni_ps *ps = ni_get_ps(rps);
7181 struct rv7xx_pl *pl;
7182 u32 current_index =
7183 (RREG32(TARGET_AND_CURRENT_PROFILE_INDEX) & CURRENT_STATE_INDEX_MASK) >>
7184 CURRENT_STATE_INDEX_SHIFT;
7185
7186 if (current_index >= ps->performance_level_count) {
7187 return 0;
7188 } else {
7189 pl = &ps->performance_levels[current_index];
7190 return pl->mclk;
7191 }
7192}
